article.story: MOREHEAD, Ky. -- — Riley Minix scored 30 points to lead Morehead State past SIU Edwardsville 79-68 on Thursday night. Minix also had 13 rebounds for the Eagles (19-5, 10-1 Ohio Valley Conference). Drew Thelwell made four 3-pointers and scored 17 with seven assists. Kalil Thomas added 15 points. Ray'Sean Taylor finished with 22 points and three steals for the Cougars (13-11, 6-5). Damarco Minor added 18 points, 13 rebounds and four assists. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
